{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 6",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-600512857544589973 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/j0rgbv-09/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=600495993187730277&sectionId=600512857544589973)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7-ANgD9Wu_text","label":"gg7-ANgD9Wu_text","default":"A note on patience:"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2L5Ik6AEj_text","label":"gg2L5Ik6AEj_text","default":"<p>I always tell my patients: <strong>the 8-week timeline is not arbitrary.</strong></p><p><br>Collagen synthesis is a biological process. It cannot be rushed. Anyone who promises you visible structural change in \"3 days\" or \"one week\" is lying to you. They're selling you temporary surface effects—hydration, mild swelling from irritation—not actual rebuilding.</p><p><br>Real structural change requires real biological time. The men who see the best results are those who trust the process and apply consistently for the full 8 weeks.</p><p><br>This is why I appreciate that Omnis offers their supply in a two-month package. It ensures you have enough product to complete the full transformation cycle without interruption.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRnxZc8qvR_text","label":"ggRnxZc8qvR_text","default":"Let me be direct with you—as I would be with any patient in my pharmacy."},{"type":"html","id":"ggojKT5i0GF_text","label":"ggojKT5i0GF_text","default":"<p>I've spent 23 years helping men navigate the confusing landscape of skincare. I've seen thousands of products come and go. I've watched men waste money on solutions that never had a chance of working.</p><p><br>And I've learned that the men who get results are the ones who stop hoping and start deciding.</p><p><br>So let me give you the same assessment I give to the men who visit my pharmacy in Rome:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxPndph-D0_text","label":"ggxPndph-D0_text","default":"The questions men ask me (and my honest answers):"},{"type":"html","id":"gguhiXK5BzI_childItem_0","label":"gguhiXK5BzI_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>\"Is this just another expensive moisturizer?\"</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXpxF9En3n_text","label":"ggXpxF9En3n_text","default":"<p>No. And the fact that you're asking tells me you've been burned before.</p><p><br>Here's how to tell the difference: Look at the mechanism.</p><p><br>A moisturizer adds water to the surface. That's all it does. The effects disappear when the water evaporates.</p><p><br>Omnis contains Retinyl Palmitate—a Vitamin A derivative that signals your cells to produce new collagen. This is structural change, not surface hydration. The effects accumulate over time because you're literally rebuilding the scaffolding of your skin.</p><p><br>If a product doesn't contain an active that stimulates collagen synthesis, it's a moisturizer. No matter what the label says.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeW77cnUjg_childItem_0","label":"ggeW77cnUjg_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>\"I&#039;ve tried Retinol before and it destroyed my skin.\"</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDZYp1BRpq_text","label":"ggDZYp1BRpq_text","default":"<p>Then you've experienced exactly why Retinyl Palmitate exists.</p><p><br>Standard Retinol—and especially prescription Tretinoin—works by forcing rapid, aggressive cell turnover. For mature skin, this is often too much. The irritation causes most men to quit before seeing results.</p><p><br>Retinyl Palmitate converts to the active form <i>inside</i> your skin, gradually, through a two-step enzymatic process. You get the same collagen-building outcome without the surface-level assault.</p><p><br>If harsh Retinol is a sledgehammer, Retinyl Palmitate is a precision instrument. Same destination, gentler path.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIExn0fks9_childItem_0","label":"ggIExn0fks9_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>\"Why should I trust an Italian product over American brands?\"</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAGD0WmdLZ_text","label":"ggAGD0WmdLZ_text","default":"<p>Because Italian pharmaceutical regulations are stricter than American cosmetic regulations.</p><p><br>The FDA classifies most skincare as \"cosmetics,\" which means minimal oversight. Companies can make broad claims with little substantiation. They can include ingredients that are banned in Europe.</p><p><br>Italian pharmaceutical standards require efficacy testing, stability testing, and ingredient purity verification. The formulation process is closer to medicine than makeup.</p><p><br>This isn't nationalism. It's regulatory reality. When I recommend a product to a patient, I need to know it meets pharmaceutical standards—not just marketing standards.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4Zul_tJJH_childItem_0","label":"gg4Zul_tJJH_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>\"How do I know this will work for MY neck?\"</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCFkMVyKRV_text","label":"ggCFkMVyKRV_text","default":"<p>You don't. Not with certainty. And anyone who guarantees specific results for your specific biology is lying to you.</p><p><br>What I can tell you is this:</p><p><br>The mechanism is sound. Retinyl Palmitate stimulates collagen production. Vitamin C stabilizes that collagen. Hyaluronic Acid protects it from enzymatic breakdown. This is established dermatological science, not speculation.</p><p><br>72,000+ men have used this formulation. 87% report visible improvement in the neck and jawline area. The probability that you'll see meaningful results is high.</p><p><br>But biology is individual. Which is why Omnis offers a 60-day guarantee. You have enough time to complete the full 8-week transformation cycle. If you don't see results, you get your money back.</p><p><br>That's as close to \"risk-free\" as medicine gets.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9GgQ6tYNM_childItem_0","label":"gg9GgQ6tYNM_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>\"$70 seems expensive for a face cream.\"</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggih4N2SYCJ_text","label":"ggih4N2SYCJ_text","default":"<p>Compared to what?</p><p><br>A drugstore moisturizer that doesn't work? Yes, it's more expensive.</p><p><br>A neck lift consultation? That's $200 just for the appointment. The procedure itself is $5,000-15,000.</p><p><br>Botox for the neck area? $300-600 per session, every 3-4 months. That's $1,200-2,400 per year, indefinitely.</p><p><br>The \"prescription-strength\" Retinol your dermatologist might recommend? $150-300 per tube, plus the office visit.</p><p><br>At $70 for a two-month supply, Omnis costs approximately $1.10 per day. That's less than your morning coffee.</p><p><br>The question isn't whether $70 is expensive. The question is: expensive compared to the alternative? Compared to doing nothing and watching your neck continue to sag?</p><p><br>I've never had a patient tell me they regretted spending $70 on something that worked.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpqo8bkoQ8_childItem_0","label":"ggpqo8bkoQ8_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>\"What if it doesn&#039;t work? What if I&#039;m wasting my money again?\"</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggu3gqC17Qk_text","label":"ggu3gqC17Qk_text","default":"<p>Then you return it and get every penny back.</p><p><br>Omnis offers a 60-day money-back guarantee. Not 30 days—60. That's specifically because the transformation timeline requires 8 weeks. They're giving you enough time to complete the full cycle before you decide.</p><p><br>If you don't see visible improvement in your neck by week 8, you contact their support team and receive a full refund. No complicated process. No \"restocking fees.\" No interrogation.</p><p><br>You're not risking $70. You're risking nothing except the time it takes to find out if this works for you.</p><p><br>And if it does work? You've solved a problem that's been bothering you every time you look in the mirror.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmTsojTDn-_text","label":"ggmTsojTDn-_text","default":"So here is the decision, as I present it to my patients:"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0Gal3XJzX_text","label":"gg0Gal3XJzX_text","default":"<p>You have two paths forward. Both are valid choices. But they lead to very different destinations.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3s9QclLZ__text","label":"gg3s9QclLZ__text","default":"<p>Path 1: Try the Italian Protocol</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGGObA0NQR_text","label":"ggGGObA0NQR_text","default":"<p>Commit to 60 days. Apply Omnis every night before bed. Give the formulation time to work—the full 8 weeks required for collagen rebuilding.</p><p><br>If it works (as it has for 72,000+ men), you'll see visible tightening in your neck. A more defined jawline. The \"turkey neck\" appearance reduced. You'll look in the mirror and see something closer to the man you still feel like inside.</p><p><br>If it doesn't work, you request a refund and you're back where you started—minus nothing except two months of trying.</p><p><br><strong>Your risk:</strong> Zero dollars (with the guarantee)</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Your potential outcome:</strong> A neck that doesn't make you self-conscious anymore</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFAFK6U4mM_text","label":"ggFAFK6U4mM_text","default":"<p>Path 2: Continue as you are</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTLaMg6PdB_text","label":"ggTLaMg6PdB_text","default":"<p>Close this page. Go back to your current routine—whether that's nothing, or a moisturizer that isn't working, or occasional consideration of expensive procedures you're not ready to commit to.</p><p><br>Your neck will continue on its current trajectory. Collagen production will continue declining at approximately 1-2% per year. The sagging will progress. The \"turkey neck\" will become more pronounced.</p><p><br>This isn't a scare tactic. It's biology. After 50, this process doesn't reverse itself without intervention.</p><p><br><strong>Your risk:</strong> Zero dollars (today)</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Your guaranteed outcome:</strong> Continued structural decline</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_e29wFawP_text","label":"gg_e29wFawP_text","default":"My professional recommendation:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcXrrxy20x_text","label":"ggcXrrxy20x_text","default":"<p>I don't tell my patients what to do. I give them information and let them decide.</p><p><br>But when they ask me directly—\"Marco, what would you do?\"—I tell them the truth:</p><p><br><strong>I would try it.</strong></p><p><br>Not because it's guaranteed to work for everyone. Nothing in medicine is guaranteed.</p><p><br>But because the mechanism is sound, the risk is zero with the guarantee, and the cost of inaction is watching yourself age in a way that bothers you.</p><p><br>I've seen too many men spend years \"thinking about it\" while their necks continued to sag. They eventually try something—often something more expensive and more invasive—and wish they'd started sooner.</p><p><br>The best time to address structural aging was 10 years ago. The second best time is now.</p><p><br>If you're still reading this, you already know something needs to change. The only question is whether you're ready to find out if this is the solution.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggG4Fx95u4C_text","label":"ggG4Fx95u4C_text","default":"If you're ready to begin the Italian Protocol:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAdEtW4dAd_text","label":"ggAdEtW4dAd_text","default":"<p>Omnis is currently offering a U.S. launch special that, frankly, makes this decision simple from a cost-benefit perspective.</p><p><br>As a pharmacist, I rarely comment on pricing. But when a formulation of this quality is available at this price point, with a full guarantee, I consider it my professional duty to mention it.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-IAllCDaZ_text","label":"gg-IAllCDaZ_text","default":"<p>4.8 out of 5 | 7,405+ Reviews</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaP2_7nBuH_text","label":"ggaP2_7nBuH_text","default":"Omnis Uomo Anti-Aging Night Cream"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSTYTa2W9N_text","label":"ggSTYTa2W9N_text","default":"<p>The Italian Formulation Recommended by Pharmacists Across Europe</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggT0Npug-g4_text","label":"ggT0Npug-g4_text","default":"<p>The Complete Three-Part System in One Application:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoS3HsedfD_childItem_0","label":"ggoS3HsedfD_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Retinyl Palmitate (Vitamin A) </strong>— The \"gentleman's Retinol.\" Signals fibroblast cells to restart collagen production without the burning, peeling, or irritation of harsh retinoids.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoS3HsedfD_childItem_1","label":"ggoS3HsedfD_childItem_1","default":"<p><strong>Stabilized Vitamin C from Sicilian Oranges </strong>— Cross-links and strengthens new collagen fibers. Remains potent until moment of application (unlike unstable Vitamin C serums).</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoS3HsedfD_childItem_2","label":"ggoS3HsedfD_childItem_2","default":"<p><strong>Hyaluronic Acid </strong>— Inhibits MMP enzymes that break down collagen. Provides deep hydration while protecting your structural investment.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvfg6mMD2k_text","label":"ggvfg6mMD2k_text","default":"<p><i>Supporting Ingredients:</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHFtVBvwoR_childItem_0","label":"ggHFtVBvwoR_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Cold-Pressed Tuscan Olive Oil</strong> — Antioxidant protection against environmental damage</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHFtVBvwoR_childItem_1","label":"ggHFtVBvwoR_childItem_1","default":"<p><strong>Hydrolyzed Rice Protein </strong>— Additional anti-aging and moisture-retention support</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHFtVBvwoR_childItem_2","label":"ggHFtVBvwoR_childItem_2","default":"<p><strong>Aloe Barbadensis — Soothing, anti-inflammatory base</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggiX4t1wA6x_text","label":"ggiX4t1wA6x_text","default":"<p><strong>Formulation Standards:</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCI_p-QkCE_childItem_0","label":"ggCI_p-QkCE_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Made in Italy 🇮🇹 </strong>— Formulated under strict Italian pharmaceutical regulations</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCI_p-QkCE_childItem_1","label":"ggCI_p-QkCE_childItem_1","default":"<p><strong>Approved by Italian Pharmacists </strong>— The #1 recommendation for men over 40</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCI_p-QkCE_childItem_2","label":"ggCI_p-QkCE_childItem_2","default":"<p><strong>Dermatologically Tested </strong>— Safe for sensitive skin, including the delicate neck area</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCI_p-QkCE_childItem_3","label":"ggCI_p-QkCE_childItem_3","default":"<p><strong>Free From:</strong> Alcohol, parabens, harsh silicones, and 1,600+ ingredients banned under EU pharmaceutical standards</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCI_p-QkCE_childItem_4","label":"ggCI_p-QkCE_childItem_4","default":"<p><strong>Night-Only Protocol </strong>— One application, 30 seconds, works while you sleep</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYOIAlKRp9_text","label":"ggYOIAlKRp9_text","default":"U.S. Launch Special: <span style=\"color:#0055B5;\">Up to 64%OFF</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEOPUHFgxh_text","label":"ggEOPUHFgxh_text","default":"<p>$24.99/Bottle</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqCOAM1KKO_text","label":"ggqCOAM1KKO_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:rgba(5,23,35,0.5);\"><s>$69.99</s></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYJJw9Jk3N_text","label":"ggYJJw9Jk3N_text","default":"<p>Save 64%</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghcLNjCJ6i_text","label":"gghcLNjCJ6i_text","default":"<p>That's six full months of supply—enough to complete the entire transformation timeline.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfInSJYpim_childItem_0","label":"ggfInSJYpim_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Less than $1.10 per day </strong>— Less than your morning coffee</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfInSJYpim_childItem_1","label":"ggfInSJYpim_childItem_1","default":"<p><strong>FREE Shipping </strong>— Direct to your door</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4dXeGg1uU_text","label":"gg4dXeGg1uU_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#0055B5;\"><strong>FREE Bonus:&nbsp;</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2Yl7q7q7O_text","label":"gg2Yl7q7q7O_text","default":"<p><strong>\"The Italian Gentleman Blueprint\"</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJjx-cHJf2_text","label":"ggJjx-cHJf2_text","default":"<p>— A $40 value. 120 pages on style, presence, and the Italian approach to aging well. (Not required reading, but my patients tell me they appreciate it.)</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbxLnK9cFV_label","label":"ggbxLnK9cFV_label","default":"<p>BEGIN THE ITALIAN PROTOCOL — RISK FREE&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAtFdV5M_I_label","label":"ggAtFdV5M_I_label","default":"<p>&gt;&gt;&gt; BEGIN THE ITALIAN PROTOCOL — RISK FREE &lt;&lt;&lt;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggZx6Pt0lx_text","label":"gggZx6Pt0lx_text","default":"The <span style=\"color:#0054B4;\">60-Day</span> Clinical Guarantee"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMtiDa3D9f_text","label":"ggMtiDa3D9f_text","default":"<p>As a pharmacist, I never recommend a product without understanding the guarantee terms. Here's what Omnis offers:</p><p><br><strong>Try it for 60 days. </strong>That's the full 8-week transformation timeline—enough time for the collagen rebuilding process to produce visible structural change.</p><p><br><strong>If you don't see results, request a full refund.</strong> Contact the support team, explain that you completed the protocol and didn't see the improvement you expected, and receive every penny back.</p><p><br>No \"restocking fees.\" No complicated return authorization process. No interrogation about why you're returning it.</p><p><br><strong>This is how confident they are in the formulation.</strong></p><p><br>In 23 years of pharmacy practice, I've learned that guarantee terms tell you everything about a company's confidence in their product. Companies that offer short windows (14 days, 30 days) know their products don't produce lasting results. They're hoping you'll forget to return it.</p><p><br>A 60-day guarantee on an 8-week protocol means they expect you to complete the full cycle and see results. They're betting on efficacy, not forgetfulness.</p><p><br><strong>Your financial risk: Zero.</strong></p>"}],
